overview:
Medical Spa MD is the premier physician community for dermatologists and plastic surgeons practicing in skin clinics, laser centers, and medspas around the world.

The development of non-surgical medical technologies has resulted in a boom in the number of locations offering non-surgical cosmetic medical treatments. Medical Spa MD is a resource for physicians and medspa professionals everywhere who are interested in new cosmetic and anti-aging medical technologies and business development.

Plastic Surgeons, Dermatologists, Aesthetic Physicians, medical providers and business professionals interested in understanding non-surgical cosmetic medicine and the business surrounding it use Medical Spa MDs resources, forums, blogs, and members only areas to make better business decisions and grow their practice.

Our members are the physician-architects and individuals behind the development of some of the current medical spa businesses models and non-surgical medical technologies.
